snippet.title: Taking My Daughter to New ChikFilA in Bloxburg Family RP
snippet.description:
In todays Roblox family Roleplay, I take my daughter Goldie to the new chikfila restaurant in Bloxburg. We order our favorite food, check out the playground and make some new friends on the way.

Check out the Chikfila by Verklas
Chick-fil-A Twitter: https://x.com/BloxyChickFilA
Chick-fil-A Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/3465453...
